    dc:description "Fig. 127. Eocanites planus (Schindewolf, 1926) from the Oberrödinghausen railway cutting. A. Lateral view and dorsal reconstruction of neotype GPIT-PV-64009 (Vöhringer Coll.) from bed 1. B. Suture line of specimen GPIT-PV-63990 (Vöhringer Coll.) from an unknown bed, at ww = 6.2 mm, wh =7.0 mm. Scale bar units= 1 mm." ;
